{{新加坡政治}}
'''國會議長'''（{{lang-en|Speaker of the Parliament}}）是[[新加坡共和国|新加坡共和国]]的[[新加坡國會|议会]]主持人，議長也是繼[[总统顾问理事会|總統顧問理事會]](CPA) 主席之後的第二位總統繼任者。新加坡至今的十任议长中，仅有两人不是议员；分别为首任议长乔治·厄勒斯爵士和第四任议长古马拉三美。<ref>{{cite web|title=Halimah Yacob to be renominated as Speaker of Parliament: 7 things you may not know about the post|url=https://www.straitstimes.com/politics/halimah-yacob-to-be-renominated-as-speaker-of-parliament-7-things-you-may-not-know-about|accessdate=2020-09-18|author=|date=2016-01-08|format=|publisher=The Straits Times 新加坡海峡时报|language=英语|author1=Lee Min Kok|website=The Straits Times|archive-date=2018-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181027185655/https://www.straitstimes.com/politics/halimah-yacob-to-be-renominated-as-speaker-of-parliament-7-things-you-may-not-know-about|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=关于国会议长 你不得不知的四点|url=https://www.zaobao.com.sg/znews/singapore/story20170807-785310|accessdate=2020-09-18|author=黄俊贤|date=2017-08-07|format=|publisher=新加坡联合早报网|language=中文|archive-date=2017-08-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170810094322/http://www.zaobao.com.sg/znews/singapore/story20170807-785310|dead-url=no}}</ref>第九任国会议长[[哈莉玛·雅各布|哈莉玛·雅各布]]是新加坡国会史上第一位女议长。<ref>{{cite web|title=哈莉玛当选新加坡总统 愿与国人“同心同行”|url=http://www.xinhuanet.com//world/2017-09/13/c_129703432.htm|accessdate=2020-09-18|publisher=新华社|author1=包雪琳（记者）|website=新华网|archive-date=2021-05-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210524165344/http://www.xinhuanet.com//world/2017-09/13/c_129703432.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[人民行动党|人民行動黨]]的[[陈川仁|陈川仁]]是现任新加坡国会议长，副議長是[[迪舒沙|迪舒沙]]及[[陳舜娘|陳舜娘]]。

== 選舉 ==
國會必須在每個新議會任期開始時選出一名議長。<ref>Constitution, Art. 40(1).</ref>議會有權決定如何選舉議長， 按照最近的傳統，通常是首相提名一個人， 然後由國會議員投票決定是否通過，通過的人選即被選為議長。<ref name="Constitution, Art. 402">Constitution, Art. 40(2).</ref>議長可以不是民選議員，但必須具備憲法規定的參選議員資格。議長不能是內閣成員或議會秘書，如果需要成為議長，就必須在當選前辭去這些職位。<ref name="ParlSpeaker">{{cite web|title=Speaker of Parliament|url=https://www.parliament.gov.sg/about-us/structure/speaker-of-parliament|access-date=7 August 2017|website=Parliament of Singapore|archive-date=2020-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200121025305/https://www.parliament.gov.sg/about-us/structure/speaker-of-parliament}}</ref>

一旦當選，除非他主動辭職、被任命為內閣部長或被取消擔任議員的資格，否則議長將持續任職直至本屆議會解散。

== 職責 ==
新加坡國會議長的角色與大多數英聯邦的立法機構角色類似。議長負責主持會議，並執行議事規則，以有序開展議會事務。在履行職責時，議長必須對所有議員保持公正和公平。<ref name="ParlSpeaker2">{{cite web|title=Speaker of Parliament|url=https://www.parliament.gov.sg/about-us/structure/speaker-of-parliament|access-date=7 August 2017|website=Parliament of Singapore|archive-date=2020-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200121025305/https://www.parliament.gov.sg/about-us/structure/speaker-of-parliament}}</ref>議長負責規範和執行辯論規則，他決定誰有發言權，及將問題提交到議會進行辯論和投票。議長並不參與辯論，但如果他是民選議員則具有投票權。<ref name="ParlSpeaker3">{{cite web|title=Speaker of Parliament|url=https://www.parliament.gov.sg/about-us/structure/speaker-of-parliament|access-date=7 August 2017|website=Parliament of Singapore|archive-date=2020-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200121025305/https://www.parliament.gov.sg/about-us/structure/speaker-of-parliament}}</ref>作為議會特權的守護者，國會議員可向議長尋求程序上的指導及裁決。<ref name="ParlSpeaker4">{{cite web|title=Speaker of Parliament|url=https://www.parliament.gov.sg/about-us/structure/speaker-of-parliament|access-date=7 August 2017|website=Parliament of Singapore|archive-date=2020-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200121025305/https://www.parliament.gov.sg/about-us/structure/speaker-of-parliament}}</ref>

國會議長在新加坡總統職位的繼任順序中排名第二。 如果總統職位空缺，總統顧問委員會主席也無法擔任該職務，議長則將代行總統職責，直至選出新總統為止。<ref>Constitution, Art. 22N.</ref>在國家禮節方面，議長與新加坡首席大法官處於同一級別。<ref name="ST20160108">{{cite news|last1=Lee|first1=Min Kok|title=Halimah Yacob to be renominated as Speaker of Parliament: 7 things you may not know about the post|url=http://www.straitstimes.com/politics/halimah-yacob-to-be-renominated-as-speaker-of-parliament-7-things-you-may-not-know-about|access-date=7 August 2017|work=The Straits Times|date=8 January 2016|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170807172539/http://www.straitstimes.com/politics/halimah-yacob-to-be-renominated-as-speaker-of-parliament-7-things-you-may-not-know-about|archive-date=7 August 2017|language=en}}</ref>

